result.name: Leisurely Veggie

reviews.text:
I had brunch with two friends at Leisurely Veggie (25th Floor) on a Thursday afternoon, there was no waiting, we were seated immediately. The service was prompt and friendly, however staff had limited English. The menu includes Chinese and English and has pictures.  I recommend the Butterfly drink (purple beverage in photo) at $40 hkd and the pizza was really good with a freshly baked dough base, although it's a bit expensive at $88 for the modest size. I loved the sesame cake! Great black sesame flavour and light in texture for a layered cake. 
Note the operating hours before visiting as we had to order, eat and leave quickly because they were closing soon.

Arrived around 8pm, some of the dishes already sold out.

Portion is small, less oil, seems healthier.

Dinner set for 6 or 12 people need to be reserved one day ago.

Restaurant suitable for 4 people or less.
A vegetarian's paradise. The mango avocado roll is a must try. I also loved the Dan Dan mi

Food quality and service getting worse
Expensive yet value is not delivered

Food here were good with much flavour and you will not feel like you are having no meat. Much variety of choices including western dishes. Some creative dishes like pizza is worth trying too. Service is attentive. I would not recommend the soup though, since it's not very good value compare with others.

我們到來食素菜，之前是食晚餐套餐，覺得環境及食物質素唔錯，所以再來食下午茶！
地方方便：渣甸中心25樓，服務友善親切！坐位舒適，更有房間比我們，可以慢慢傾。
下午茶是2:30-4:30，食物有8個餐，有意粉、麵食、點心、手卷配多士、甜品、班㦸等等，選擇多又配上餐飲，現在HSBC或恆生信用卡星期一至五滿250更有95折，變相唔洗加一了
賣相同味道都唔錯，我點了擔擔麵，麻醬好香，辣味可自選，麵份量好足夠！餐飲點了五殼杏仁牛脆，健康又有口感！
交通方便，地方整潔，食物美味。

Arrived around 8pm, some of the dishes already sold out.

Portion is small, less oil, seems healthier.

Dinner set for 6 or 12 people need to be reserved one day ago.

Restaurant suitable for 4 people or less.

result.name: 野將 Ginger Ginger

reviews.text: 食物質素唔差,味道也不錯。坐位位置相當闊大舒服
極差的服務，返工嚟食個lunch 等了45分鐘，最後咩都無食落肚就走左，浪費時間，永遠不會再幫襯，不知所謂，等了20分鐘時，已經問要等幾耐，等到第30分鐘，仲話嚟緊出緊，到等45分鐘，終於忍唔住，我同事得5分鐘，食一知個熱既湯麵，不知所謂。垃圾服務。不要只為錢，罔顧客人既感受同需要，做唔到出唔到單，講一聲就可以！
十分美味的新派東南亞菜，已經第四次光顧了。

We ordered the food via deliveroo and it was delivered late. They really care about the customers and kept apologising for the late (which was not their fault at all).

The food was still super delicious although it arrived late.

Highly recommended for the great service and food!
食物的質素不錯，新鮮及味美，服務員也很有禮貌，值得推薦予大家作新嘗試! 我將來定必會再次惠顧此小店的!
